{"tid":2100531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"熊熊「一次中2點」承認性慾強又好色！ 羞曝：男友想每天一次也OK","createTime":"2020-07-09T06:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T12:01:09.000Z","uid":4646,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0893c163715763740e9d8abce05a4a19421aca7c","tid":2100531,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"記者張筱涵／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n藝人熊熊（卓毓彤）擁有G罩杯的好身材，近年來積極挑戰主持和演戲受到粉絲支持，日前和宛宛兒討論到性方面話題，大方承認自己對男友就會很好色，只要對方要求每天一次的頻率也是很OK。<br />\n<br />\n宛宛兒透露身邊處女座的男生都好色，同樣身為處女座的熊熊認同也承認自己好色：「我覺得每個星座男生都很好色，可是好色很OK，你不要亂色就好，內射就要負責。」她認為性是感情的調劑品，自己對男友很好色且對方如果要每天一次也很OK。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4988/4988202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4988%2F4988202.jpg&h=8e65b852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲熊熊承認好色並會滿足男友需求。（圖／翻攝自宛宛兒YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n雖然熊熊這樣說，但個性害羞所以也不會非常主動，通常都會用暗示的方式讓男友了解需求，而她認為水瓶座的男女生是最不好色的，最後談到「胸部大的女生性慾比較強」，害羞笑說自己是這樣沒有錯，並透露了敏感帶是耳朵和脖子，偏好體位是在上面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4988/4988202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4988%2F4988202.jpg&h=8e65b852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲熊熊羞曝喜歡的體位。（圖／翻攝自宛宛兒YouTube）"},{"pid":"98d44e17c5bccf781f8de7a56eb80dc42a785bca","tid":2100531,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_8P-oVyhdXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_8P-oVyhdXo&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=df3f72d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_8P-oVyhdXo</a>"},{"pid":"79acdbdbd35b7c89686c4b59672d114b6be99717","tid":2100531,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1755176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1755176&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmrXqul